videos.description: Jordan Horston makes a nice pass to Rae Burrell, who knocks down the 3-pointer for the Lady Vols.
videos.headline: Burrell sinks 3 for Tennessee

videos.description: Texas A&M dribbles the ball around and Chennedy Carter ends up with it, connecting for a 3-pointer from the corner.

videos.description: Rae Burrell fights off a defender and tosses up a layup while drawing a foul.

videos.description: Jordan Horston makes a clear path to the basket and finishes with the layup.
